abstract: Gene Palmer, an officer at Clinton Correctional Facility, described giving Richard Matt a screwdriver and pliers in exchange for a dozen elaborate paintings by the inmate.

lead_paragraph: PLATTSBURGH, N.Y. — The two convicted killers who broke out of a maximum-security prison in northern New York this month made their escape using rudimentary electrical and engineering skills, stealth and a canny ability to manipulate members of the prison staff.

abstract: A week after Representative Pelosi helped derail one of President Obama’s most important legislative priorities, the two spoke to the nation’s mayors on Friday within moments of each other.
snippet: A week after Representative Pelosi helped derail one of President Obama’s most important legislative priorities, the two spoke to the nation’s mayors on Friday within moments of each other.
lead_paragraph: SAN FRANCISCO — Days after Representative Nancy Pelosi helped derail one of President Obama’s most important legislative priorities, the two shared a stage, a solarium and some tight smiles on Friday as they spoke to the nation’s mayors and then at an exclusive fund-raiser.

abstract: Kia abandons bargain basement pricing for something better: a crossover with broad appeal.
snippet: Kia abandons bargain basement pricing for something better: a crossover with broad appeal.
lead_paragraph: REMEMBER when Kia was all about cheap generic economy cars? Today, its design team is led by former Audi and Cadillac rock stars (Peter Schreyer and Tom Kearns ), and among its most popular vehicles are the family-size Optima and Sorento.
headline_main: Video Review: With the Sorento, Kia Moves to the Top Shelf
headline_print_headline: With the Sorento, Kia Moves to the Top Shelf

abstract: The first lady has been opening up about her own struggles and the “insults and slights” that even living in the White House has not protected her family from.
snippet: The first lady has been opening up about her own struggles and the “insults and slights” that even living in the White House has not protected her family from.
lead_paragraph: CHICAGO — She looked around and saw herself three decades ago, young and uncertain, from a part of town where success is a struggle, not a birthright. She knew what they had been through, what it was like to take the long way home to avoid gangs, what it was like when the family strained to make ends meet.

abstract: The unit best known for killing Osama bin Laden has been converted into a global manhunting machine with limited outside oversight.
snippet: The unit best known for killing Osama bin Laden has been converted into a global manhunting machine with limited outside oversight.
lead_paragraph: They have plotted deadly missions from secret bases in the badlands of Somalia. In Afghanistan, they have engaged in combat so intimate that they have emerged soaked in blood that was not their own. On clandestine raids in the dead of the night, their weapons of choice have ranged from customized carbines to primeval tomahawks.
